Type: Music Concert

Genre: Classical Orchestra

Date and Time: December 2, 2025, 7:30 PM

Location: Royal Albert Hall, London

Details:
A magical evening of classical music performed by the renowned London Symphony Orchestra under the open sky. Expect a repertoire of masterpieces by Beethoven, Mozart, and Tchaikovsky. The event will include solo performances by virtuoso violinist Anne Sophie Mutter. The venue offers reserved seating and lawn access for a more relaxed experience.

Highlights: Live orchestra, renowned soloists, picturesque outdoor setup.

Tickets: Prices range from $50 to $200; available at Royal Albert Hall’s website.
